OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1774894265
OL,3,CCrackdown on illegal liftshares and
OL,4,CPFAS delays - this week's States
OL,5,Croundup
OL,7,FThe States of Jersey have voted to
OL,8,Fcrackdown on unlicenced taxi services,
OL,9,Fbut failed to introduce new
OL,10,Flegislation to reduce PFAS levels in
OL,11,Fthe island's water, in their
OL,12,Fpenultimate week of debate before the
OL,13,Fend of their electoral term.
OL,15,FThe Assembly considered a wide range
OL,16,Fof propositions alongside their
OL,17,Famendments, as they sought to work
OL,18,Fthrough all outstanding issues before
OL,19,Fadjourning next week to prepare for
OL,20,Fthe election in June.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/17
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1774894265
OL,3,CCrackdown on illegal liftshares and
OL,4,CPFAS delays - this week's States
OL,5,Croundup
OL,7,FThe most contentious decision of the
OL,8,Fweek was the States' vote to keep
OL,9,Fcurrent guidelines on transgender
OL,10,Fchildren in Jersey schools.
OL,11,FPoliticians rejected Deputy Sir Deputy
OL,12,FPhilip Bailhache's proposition for
OL,13,Fteachers to take a "neutral" and
OL,14,F"watching, waiting approach" to gender-
OL,15,Fquestioning students.
OL,17,FIllegal Taxis Crackdown
OL,19,FJersey residents offering illegal taxi
OL,20,Flifts for money could face a fine of
OL,21,Fup to #10,000 by June 2027.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/17
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1774894265
OL,3,CCrackdown on illegal liftshares and
OL,4,CPFAS delays - this week's States
OL,5,Croundup
OL,7,FThere will either be an update to the
OL,8,FMotor Traffic (Jersey) Law 1935, or
OL,9,Fthe creation of other new statutory
OL,10,Foffences in separate legislation
OL,11,Fenabling the prosecution of illegal
OL,12,Ftaxi services.
OL,14,FOffering payment for a lift will also
OL,15,Fbe a criminal offence liable to a fine
OL,16,Fof up to #1,000.
OL,18,FThe new law aims to challenge a rise
OL,19,Fin unlicensed taxi drivers, who
OL,20,Fusually offer lifts through Facebook
OL,21,Fgroups such as 'Jersey lifts'.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/17
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1774894265
OL,3,CCrackdown on illegal liftshares and
OL,4,CPFAS delays - this week's States
OL,5,Croundup
OL,7,FDeputy Catherine Curtis, who lodged
OL,8,Fthe proposition, told ITV News in
OL,9,FFebruary the rise of illegal rides has
OL,10,F"really got out of hand", and has gone
OL,11,Ffurther than just offering lift shares.
OL,13,F"People are earning their living from
OL,14,Fit. They're not paying tax or social
OL,15,Fsecurity, they're not insured, and
OL,16,Fthey haven't had DBS checks, so you
OL,17,Fcould be getting a lift from anyone,"
OL,18,FDeputy Curtis explained.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/17
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1774894265
OL,3,CCrackdown on illegal liftshares and
OL,4,CPFAS delays - this week's States
OL,5,Croundup
OL,7,F"Taxi drivers have to meet various
OL,8,Fstandards, including customer care and
OL,9,Fdisability awareness - their cars are
OL,10,Fchecked once a year for safety, and
OL,11,Fare expensively insured to cover any
OL,12,Faccidents."
OL,14,FPFAS Levels
OL,16,FPFAS are a group of approximately
OL,17,F15,000 synthetic 'forever chemicals'.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/17
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1774894265
OL,3,CCrackdown on illegal liftshares and
OL,4,CPFAS delays - this week's States
OL,5,Croundup
OL,7,FWhile the World Health Organisation
OL,8,F(WHO) has not yet completed its own
OL,9,Fassessment of the health risks
OL,10,Fassociated with PFAS, the UK
OL,11,Fgovernment has warned there is:
OL,12,F"growing concern over potential health
OL,13,Frisks and irreversible environmental
OL,14,Fcontamination."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/17
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1774894265
OL,3,CCrackdown on illegal liftshares and
OL,4,CPFAS delays - this week's States
OL,5,Croundup
OL,7,FWork to legislate a reduction in
OL,8,FJersey's PFAS levels has been ongoing,
OL,9,Fand in January an independent
OL,10,Fscientific advisory panel recommended
OL,11,Fcutting the island's current level of
OL,12,F12 nanograms per litre to a legal
OL,13,Flimit of 4 nanograms per litre.
OL,15,FEnvironment Minister, Deputy Steve
OL,16,FLuce, submitted a proposition to
OL,17,Fintroduce Jersey's limits accordingly,
OL,18,Fand for this to "be achieved within
OL,19,Ffive years."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/17
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1774894265
OL,3,CCrackdown on illegal liftshares and
OL,4,CPFAS delays - this week's States
OL,5,Croundup
OL,7,FIn the States Assembly on Wednesday
OL,8,F(25 March), Deputy Luce read out the
OL,9,Fprinciples of new PFAS legislation,
OL,10,Fwhich were then agreed on, but will
OL,11,Fnot be voted on until the next States
OL,12,FAssembly convenes.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/17
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1774894265
OL,3,CCrackdown on illegal liftshares and
OL,4,CPFAS delays - this week's States
OL,5,Croundup
OL,7,FThe legislation was called in by
OL,8,Fscrutiny, as the panel need to
OL,9,Ffinalise issues with the proposed
OL,10,Flegislation, including the cost of
OL,11,Fintroducing any new PFAS limit. It
OL,12,Fcomes after Jersey Water said bringing
OL,13,Fthe current limit down to 4 nanograms
OL,14,Fper litre could cost between #140
OL,15,Fmillion and #210 million, raising
OL,16,Fconcerns that islanders' water bills
OL,17,Fcould be doubled as a result.
OL,19,FThe result is that, for now, no
OL,20,Flegislative change has occurred.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/17
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1774894265
OL,3,CCrackdown on illegal liftshares and
OL,4,CPFAS delays - this week's States
OL,5,Croundup
OL,7,FJersey's average is already far lower
OL,8,Fthan UK guidance, which aims to keep
OL,9,FPFAS levels to less than 100 nanograms
OL,10,Fper litre, with the EU's legal limit
OL,11,Fset at a total of 500 nanograms per
OL,12,Flitre.
OL,14,FBusinesses Accepting Cash
OL,16,FFrom January 2028, all businesses in
OL,17,FJersey will be required by law to
OL,18,Faccept cash.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/17
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1774894265
OL,3,CCrackdown on illegal liftshares and
OL,4,CPFAS delays - this week's States
OL,5,Croundup
OL,7,F31 States members voted in favour of
OL,8,Fthe motion to keep notes and coins
OL,9,Fvalid, with 8 against and 2 abstained.
OL,11,FDeputy Montford Tadier, who brought
OL,12,Fthe proposition to the States,
OL,13,Fcelebrated the new law: "We're not
OL,14,Fsaying people have to use cash, but it
OL,15,Fsays that we're an inclusive society
OL,16,Fby giving the customer the option of
OL,17,Fdifferent payment methods as they see
OL,18,Ffit.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/17
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1774894265
OL,3,CCrackdown on illegal liftshares and
OL,4,CPFAS delays - this week's States
OL,5,Croundup
OL,7,F"Tourists often like to take cash out
OL,8,Ffor small spends, but there are also
OL,9,Flots of people without bank accounts
OL,10,Fwho need to use cash."
OL,12,FGender Neutral Inheritance Laws
OL,14,FCurrent legislation states that the
OL,15,F'principal heir' of an estate is the
OL,16,Foldest male in a family - a concept
OL,17,Fwhich is now being replaced by a
OL,18,Fgender-neutral approach.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/17
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1774894265
OL,3,CCrackdown on illegal liftshares and
OL,4,CPFAS delays - this week's States
OL,5,Croundup
OL,7,FCourts will also now be allowed to
OL,8,Fappoint someone to manage an estate,
OL,9,Fother than those currently entitled to
OL,10,Fdo so.
OL,12,FAnother key change is that spouses and
OL,13,Fcivil partners will be able to
OL,14,Fcontinue living in their family home,
OL,15,Feven if it has not been specifically
OL,16,Fleft to them in a will.
OL,18,FOther New Laws
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G13/17
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1774894265
OL,3,CCrackdown on illegal liftshares and
OL,4,CPFAS delays - this week's States
OL,5,Croundup
OL,7,FGovernment loans will now be available
OL,8,Ffor fisheries, after a proposition by
OL,9,Fthe Minister for Sustainable Economic
OL,10,FDevelopment, Deputy Kirsten Morel, was
OL,11,Funanimously approved by the States.
OL,13,FCurrent legislation only allows such
OL,14,Floans for agriculture.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G14/17
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38715
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1774894265
OL,3,CCrackdown on illegal liftshares and
OL,4,CPFAS delays - this week's States
OL,5,Croundup
OL,7,FDeputy Morel also successfully
OL,8,Fproposed to update Jersey's shipping
OL,9,Flaws, after an independent audit in
OL,10,F2022 found that Jersey's maritime
OL,11,Flegislation did not accurately reflect
OL,12,Fthe international conventions it has
OL,13,Fsigned up to or joined as a member of
OL,14,Fthe International Maritime
OL,15,FOrganisation (IMO).
OL,17,FUnder the new legislation, the
OL,18,Fisland's laws will be updated to
OL,19,F"properly reflect" these conventions.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G15/17
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38716
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1774894265
OL,3,CCrackdown on illegal liftshares and
OL,4,CPFAS delays - this week's States
OL,5,Croundup
OL,7,FThe proposition suggested the new
OL,8,Flegislation will improve Jersey's
OL,9,Fstanding within the Red Ensign Group
OL,10,Fand wider international maritime
OL,11,Fcommunity.
OL,13,FStates members themselves will also be
OL,14,Fsubject to different rules, as new
OL,15,Fguidelines will state that any Deputy
OL,16,Fwho is charged with a serious violent
OL,17,For sexual offence in Jersey will
OL,18,Fautomatically be temporarily excluded
OL,19,Ffrom the States.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G16/17
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
